{"tid":2367997,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–誰可笑到最後","createTime":"2021-01-15T19:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T05:57:57.000Z","uid":38861,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"06caa7595d6ac75c91d3bf0795372f65169baef5","tid":2367997,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T19:41:17.000Z","msg":"人無事，才可以開世界的香檳，以及笑到最後。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9csbhHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9csbhHQ.jpg&h=869dd382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但身體的細胞又可唔可以與我們笑到最後呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）一個70kg重的人，平均有30兆人體細胞，人體細胞合起上來的重量約佔46kg。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqyBtPx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqyBtPx.jpg&h=07e24ed1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）較為短命的細胞分別為腸道表皮的細胞及兩款免疫系統細胞(Monocytes, neutrophils)，只有2-5日的壽命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJU84nV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJU84nV.png&h=16606bd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅血球就平均有110日壽命，而脂肪細胞就有4500日的壽命!<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）較為長壽的細胞分別以萬日起跳，分別為心臟肌肉細胞（60,000日壽命）、肌肉細胞:（20,000日壽命）和神經細胞（300,000日壽命），實為相對上可以同我們笑到最後的三大同伴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALvwhHX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALvwhHX.jpg&h=93e8e483&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，你今日不妨可以跟心臟的肌肉分享一下耀宗的趣事，讓他笑足至少6萬日，苦中作樂。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=0bd537c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=4fd176bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-01182-9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-020-01182-9&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFjWqReVd2N9LFFOFvvIGphw%3D&h=2afb7f98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41591-020-01182-9</a>"},{"pid":"d87182c388a070bb22ca03c64dbc0358c5d28cdd","tid":2367997,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T19:43:12.000Z","msg":"薯仔次次都3am出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f82b4bd82a6a1668a068606cf8960bb52d9d20","tid":2367997,"uid":34119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T19:45:21.000Z","msg":"耀宗的趣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7615bce828cea5b25b887627d452e462529cca97","tid":2367997,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d87182c388a070bb22ca03c64dbc0358c5d28cdd","tid":2367997,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T19:43:12.000Z","msg":"薯仔次次都3am出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T19:46:41.000Z","msg":"人在野，有時差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"